Class PairObjThreeDouble

    public class PairObjThreeDouble
extends PairObjTwoDouble
    utility class extends PairObjTwoDouble with a third double. Used in the tests.sic package to return the optimal value of a function as well as a lower bound of it and the fixed ordering costs at the optimal review period. Notes:
    • 20191227: added hashCode() method.
